    • Method Detail

      • getPreferredPrefix

        public static String getPreferredPrefix(String namespace,
                        String defaultValue)
        Returns the preferred prefix for the given namespace URI.
        Parameters:
        namespace - The namespace URI for which the prefix needs to be found. Can not be null.
        defaultValue - The default prefix to returned if the given namespace is not recognized, or null.
        Returns:
        The prefix inferred from the namespace URI, or null if the given namespace is unrecognized and the defaultValue is null.
